profile_positions.description:
I did a one year internship at TomTom head office in Amsterdam supporting the Corporate Communications department which consists of the sub departments Public Relations, Events and Internal Communications. This business experience has further developed my abilities to work under pressure, find quick solutions to unexpected situations and successfully lead projects on my own. 

During my internship I have successfully:

- contributed to the organization of TomTom's presence at IFA (Internationale Funkausstellung); Consumer Electronics Show in Berlin in September 2009 and 2010;
- contributed to the organization of TomTom VIP event in April 2010 in Amsterdam;
- led the organization of the internal TomTom Group Product Fairs in TomTom Amsterdam Rembrandtplein and Eindhoven offices;
- led the organization of the TomTom internal Tombola Auction January 2010.
- assisted in the development of a global PR plan on launching Star Wars voices on TomTom devices;
- contributed to the organization and execution of a TomTom HD Traffic PR stand at Hazeldonk, July 2010;
- attained a Marketing workshop on the topic: "Understanding Consumer needs and wants"
